title: Official Launch of Zanetor Rawlings Campaign (VIDEO)
text: Daughter of former president Jerry Rawlings, Zanetor Rawlings has formally launched her campaign as NDC aspirant for Klottey Korle constituency. Thousands of supporters thronged and converged at Asylum Down roundabout to support Zanetor Rawlings who was hosting a health walk yesterday. Zanetor and her supportes walked from Asylum Down, pass through Accra Central main road, then finally stopped at Osu Mandela Park. Present at the health walk were Zanetor’s sisters, Yaa Asantewaa and Amina Rawlings.
